<subSubSection pageId="101" pageNumber="859" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="101.[1396,2607,2291,3231]" pageId="101" pageNumber="859">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1398,1753,2962,2995]" pageId="101" pageNumber="859">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. Considered rare, and its restricted distribution of the 
<collectingRegion box="[2015,2062,3001,3034]" country="Nigeria" name="Rivers" pageId="101" pageNumber="859">Rio</collectingRegion>
Balsas Basin represents an extent of occurrence of only ¢. 
<quantity box="[1698,1818,3041,3074]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.7" pageId="101" pageNumber="859" unit="km" value="6700.0">6700 km</quantity>
®. The development of a dam in the area is leading to habitat loss, changes in forest cover, and changes in river cycles.
</paragraph>
